{"tid":1252261,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下 i7 8750h 問題","createTime":"2019-06-23T02:13:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T04:14:43.000Z","uid":45801,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"806f78e026b99beb059edb398c2168e76b23c5df","tid":1252261,"uid":45801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T02:13:01.000Z","msg":"早兩日買左部新 dell g5<br />\ni7 8750h + 2060 6gb<br />\n主要 cpu 一開機已經 60-70 度，普通上網已經過 70 度<br />\n室溫大概 23 度，有開細冷氣<br />\n打機接近 90 度，有時超過添"},{"pid":"02faa76c9c939830c46a774deaa733753a800ec9","tid":1252261,"uid":45801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T02:13:53.000Z","msg":"請教一個是否正常，有冇咩降溫方法？"},{"pid":"cdc03451f565369838d79a4382209db123270bb2","tid":1252261,"uid":77771,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T02:21:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Undervolt 簡單教學:<br />\n<br />\n一部LAPTOP新買返嚟，除咗快手裝GAME同DL 鹹片之外，其實應該試咗部機CPU 可以UNDERVOLT 幾多先<br />\n<br />\n因為咩LAPTOP 都好，最大的敵人就係散熱，散熱做唔好會直接影響部機的效能<br />\n<br />\n一般LAPTOP 出廠時，廠方都會SET 到電壓比正常需要的高，一來可以保證穩定性，二來廠方先無咁好心機同你慢慢逐粒摸，所以CPU 降咗電就可以減少發熱。<br />\n<br />\nUNDERVOLT 主要有兩個SOFTWARE:<br />\nINTEL EXTREME TUNING UTILITY (XTU) <br />\nTHROTTLESTOP<br />\n (p.s. xtu最新version只support k版desktop u, 如有需要用係laptop要搵返以前version)<br />\n<br />\nXTU 我都用過吓，但我覺得介面無咁USER FDLY<br />\n所以我用THROTTLESTOP:<br />\n介面就係咁簡單:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8JemJW3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8JemJW3.png&h=88263ea6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCLICK 入去 &quot;FIVR&quot; 就會入咗呢度:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/77B0ZvY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F77B0ZvY.png&h=0fe69f85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中間FIVR CONTROL 有 得揀CPU CORE 同CPU CACHE<br />\n降咗佢哋基本上達成降溫目的<br />\n<br />\nCLICK 咗UNLOCK ADJUSTABLE VOLTAGE<br />\n再因應你CPU 選擇降幾多<br />\n正常大路CPU 都會有人討論你粒CPU 可以降幾多<br />\n圖中例子就係8750H CPU CORE 同CPU CACHE 各減150mv<br />\n<br />\n起手個陣你係淆底就先試-100mv，然後試吓STRESS TEST 吓部機，HANG 機或者BSOD 就即係你降過龍，要加返少少電</blockquote>"},{"pid":"29e663b8857396dfcb61af37f50d175df44a52d7","tid":1252261,"uid":45801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdc03451f565369838d79a4382209db123270bb2","tid":1252261,"uid":77771,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T02:21:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Undervolt 簡單教學:<br />\n<br />\n一部LAPTOP新買返嚟，除咗快手裝GAME同DL 鹹片之外，其實應該試咗部機CPU 可以UNDERVOLT 幾多先<br />\n<br />\n因為咩LAPTOP 都好，最大的敵人就係散熱，散熱做唔好會直接影響部機的效能<br />\n<br />\n一般LAPTOP 出廠時，廠方都會SET 到電壓比正常需要的高，一來可以保證穩定性，二來廠方先無咁好心機同你慢慢逐粒摸，所以CPU 降咗電就可以減少發熱。<br />\n<br />\nUNDERVOLT 主要有兩個SOFTWARE:<br />\nINTEL EXTREME TUNING UTILITY (XTU) <br />\nTHROTTLESTOP<br />\n (p.s. xtu最新version只support k版desktop u, 如有需要用係laptop要搵返以前version)<br />\n<br />\nXTU 我都用過吓，但我覺得介面無咁USER FDLY<br />\n所以我用THROTTLESTOP:<br />\n介面就係咁簡單:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8JemJW3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8JemJW3.png&h=88263ea6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCLICK 入去 &quot;FIVR&quot; 就會入咗呢度:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/77B0ZvY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F77B0ZvY.png&h=0fe69f85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中間FIVR CONTROL 有 得揀CPU CORE 同CPU CACHE<br />\n降咗佢哋基本上達成降溫目的<br />\n<br />\nCLICK 咗UNLOCK ADJUSTABLE VOLTAGE<br />\n再因應你CPU 選擇降幾多<br />\n正常大路CPU 都會有人討論你粒CPU 可以降幾多<br />\n圖中例子就係8750H CPU CORE 同CPU CACHE 各減150mv<br />\n<br />\n起手個陣你係淆底就先試-100mv，然後試吓STRESS TEST 吓部機，HANG 機或者BSOD 就即係你降過龍，要加返少少電</blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T02:28:14.000Z","msg":"多謝膠爸解答，你有咁多新玩具，一定信你😂<br />\n想問多小小，通常這操作會影響保養嗎？<br />\n原理係透過 Windows 做？定 BIOS ？<br />\n如果係 Windows 做，理論上刪左 Throttlestop 或 洗機，係咪會自動 reset 番？"},{"pid":"a356a2a2e5bdbd7a995d04798c21f3a43d4715d3","tid":1252261,"uid":22817,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T02:39:49.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.p